## Getting Started

First, ensure you have your dependencies installed:

```bash
bun install
```

Start the application in development mode:

```bash
bun run start:dev
```

## Available Scripts

- `bun run start:dev` - Watches for file changes and restarts the application.
- `bun run build` - Compiles your TypeScript code down to JavaScript.
- `bun run test` - Runs your application tests.

## Nemesis CLI

Need to scaffold new components? Use the CLI!

```bash
nemesis generate controller my-feature
nemesis generate service my-feature
```

## Learn More

Check out the [NemesisJS Documentation](https://github.com/nemesisjs/nemesis) to learn more about the framework features, Dependency Injection, and Routing decorators.
